videos.description: Boise State RB Ryan Wolpin scored his first career TD by finding the goal line from five yards out as the Broncos jump to an early 7-0 lead against Virginia.
videos.headline: Broncos stampede downfield for first-drive TD

videos.description: Virginia RB Jordan Ellis powers the ball on third down into the end zone from two yards out to tie Boise State at 7-7 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Ellis follows blocker for Virginia TD

videos.description: Virginia QB Kurt Benkert connects with Andre Levrone on a 30-yard TD pass to give Virginia a 14-7 lead over Boise State late in the first half.
videos.headline: Benkert finds Levrone behind Broncos' defense for TD

videos.description: The Broncos attempt to fool the Virginia special teams unit but drop the snap giving Virginia excellent field position.
videos.headline: Boise State botches fake punt

videos.description: Virginia QB Kurt Benkert completes a slant route to WR Doni Dowling for a 27-yard score following a failed Boise State fake punt.
videos.headline: Virginia capitalizes on field position with quick strike

videos.description: Boise State's Jake Roh takes the direct snap and is hit in the backfield, but spins and fights his way to the goal line against Virginia.
videos.headline: Roh rolls in for TD

videos.description: Virginia coach Bronco Mendenhall comments on QB Kurt Benkert's first-half success.
videos.headline: Coach Mendenhall likes his team's fast start

videos.description: Andre Levrone hauls in a 64-yard TD dart from QB Kurt Benkert. Levrone has two of Benkert's three TD passes.
videos.headline: Virginia WR sprints past Broncos' secondary for long TD catch

videos.description: Virginia RB Olamide Zaccheaus finds the corner and sprints 56 yards for the touchdown as the Cavaliers take a 35-14 lead against Boise State in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Zaccheaus extends Virginia's lead with long TD dash

videos.description: Virginia's lead grows in Boise as Jordan Ellis rushes for a goal-line TD bringing the Cavaliers' lead to 42-14 against the Broncos.
videos.headline: Ellis rushes for second touchdown

videos.description: Boise State WR Cedrick Wilson focuses to make a juggling catch and get one foot down in bounds on a 35-yard reception.
videos.headline: Wilson makes circus sideline catch

videos.description: The Cavaliers' defense hit Broncos QB Brett Rypien as he throws and safety Brenton Nelson comes up with the interception as the Cavaliers lead 42-14 in the fourth.
videos.headline: Virginia defense brings pressure, forces INT

videos.description: Boise State's QB Montell Cozart picks up the dropped snap, spins and throws a 40-yard TD to Cedrick Wilson against Virginia late in a decided 42-23 loss.
videos.headline: Cozart drops snap, throws TD

videos.description: Cavaliers' QB Kurt Benkert has thrown for 10 touchdowns and only one interception thus far this season and his team is prepared to begin conference play next week after a big win on the blue turf in Boise.
videos.headline: Benkert and Virginia offense finding rhythm
